WEBVTT

00:27.680 --> 00:30.160
This is beautiful. So elegant.

00:38.560 --> 00:40.720
The hot water's in the kettle for washing.

00:40.800 --> 00:41.840
It's late.

00:41.920 --> 00:44.080
Mrs. Fan, you should rest early.

00:44.920 --> 00:46.040
Thank you, Fuling.

00:51.400 --> 00:52.520
What do you think?

00:54.960 --> 00:55.880
It's lovely.

01:06.840 --> 01:10.520
So this is the surprise Qian meant.

01:19.000 --> 01:21.320
FORTUNE

01:25.560 --> 01:26.600
There's hot water on the table.

01:26.680 --> 01:27.880
Wash up first.

01:35.880 --> 01:36.720
All right.

02:48.400 --> 02:49.640
Wait.

02:49.720 --> 02:51.040
Pour it in here instead.

02:51.120 --> 02:52.680
Mine's already gone cold.

03:06.080 --> 03:07.040
Into the basin?

03:30.920 --> 03:32.080
You are not into foot baths?

03:41.680 --> 03:42.720
I…

03:42.800 --> 03:45.040
I don't know what you're used to,

03:45.120 --> 03:48.480
but in my house, we share one basin.

03:52.240 --> 03:55.560
If that doesn't suit you,
I can ask Fuling to heat another kettle.

03:56.080 --> 03:58.600
No need. That's not what I meant.

04:01.400 --> 04:03.600
I'll rinse off outside with cold water.

04:03.680 --> 04:04.720
Cold water?

04:05.240 --> 04:07.240
Using cold water in weather like this?

04:07.760 --> 04:08.880
You'll catch a chill.

04:09.720 --> 04:10.720
I'm used to it.

04:29.240 --> 04:31.120
There's only one bed.

04:35.160 --> 04:36.600
You and Ning sleep.

04:36.680 --> 04:37.920
I'll step out for a bit.

04:42.080 --> 04:44.800
You can't stand outside all night.

04:45.680 --> 04:48.840
Fuling said this is the only room left.

04:50.080 --> 04:50.960
It's fine.

04:53.360 --> 04:55.640
I'll ask one of the inn boys
if I can squeeze in

04:55.720 --> 04:56.760
for the night.

05:09.800 --> 05:10.640
I'll head out.

05:29.840 --> 05:31.880
What did I mess up?

05:34.080 --> 05:35.760
Was it because of that sack?

05:38.160 --> 05:39.680
Or the foot bath?

05:41.160 --> 05:42.680
Is soaking feet that frightening?

07:12.240 --> 07:16.760
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

07:43.800 --> 07:45.640
Mr. Yan, it's very late.

07:45.720 --> 07:47.160
Why aren't you in your room?

07:48.880 --> 07:50.680
She's with Ning. It would be inconvenient.

07:52.800 --> 07:54.560
That was my oversight.

07:55.240 --> 07:57.360
All the staff rooms are shared.

07:57.960 --> 08:00.520
But there's one fellow
whose snoring is unbearable.

08:00.600 --> 08:03.240
No one can sleep
in the same room with him.

08:03.880 --> 08:04.840
If you don't mind,

08:05.920 --> 08:07.240
you can use his room tonight.

08:08.600 --> 08:09.480
I don't mind.

08:43.120 --> 08:43.960
You truly mean

08:44.680 --> 08:46.640
to leave the Fan sisters behind?

08:47.200 --> 08:50.120
If you part now,
meeting again will not be easy.

08:51.520 --> 08:53.080
How could I take them with me?

08:54.440 --> 08:55.440
Bring them to the front lines?

08:55.520 --> 08:57.000
Sleep in the open,

08:57.080 --> 08:59.200
live with blades at our throats?

08:59.280 --> 09:01.440
Precisely because battle is merciless,

09:02.440 --> 09:05.840
you need a woman
who can bear the Xie family name.

09:07.400 --> 09:08.280
In my view,

09:09.440 --> 09:10.800
she is no weakling.

09:36.720 --> 09:37.640
She is great.

09:38.840 --> 09:40.920
She is stronger
than many highborn daughters.

09:42.400 --> 09:44.160
But I only wish to see her grow

09:45.040 --> 09:47.480
as she is now, wild as grass.

09:49.240 --> 09:53.160
The burden of a great clan's matron
would only bind her.

10:24.440 --> 10:26.360
Wake up. Wake up.

10:31.680 --> 10:33.320
Scholar Song? Quick, help him up.

10:34.520 --> 10:35.440
Careful.

10:36.520 --> 10:38.840
Sir, you're covered in wounds.

10:38.920 --> 10:40.560
Were you robbed?

10:42.360 --> 10:43.200
One.

10:43.960 --> 10:44.880
Two.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.000
Three.

10:47.920 --> 10:49.520
-Last night… I think…
-Four.

10:50.760 --> 10:52.040
-Last night…
-Five.

10:53.360 --> 10:54.960
-I think a child hacked at me.
-Six.

11:01.120 --> 11:04.360
VERNAL VITALITY. AUSPICIOUS ABUNDANCE

11:23.480 --> 11:24.920
You didn't sleep at all, did you?

11:30.760 --> 11:33.360
I told you that lad snores like thunder.

11:33.440 --> 11:35.240
He must have kept you up.

11:35.920 --> 11:37.680
I'll fetch some tea.

11:43.400 --> 11:44.640
Go lie down a while.

11:45.440 --> 11:48.160
Ning is being looked after
by the inn boys.

11:48.240 --> 11:51.560
You truly mean
to leave the Fan sisters behind?

11:53.440 --> 11:56.200
If you part now,
meeting again will not be easy.

11:59.440 --> 12:01.160
Did you hear me?

12:03.520 --> 12:04.400
I did.

12:05.160 --> 12:06.240
Where's your mind wandering?

12:07.680 --> 12:08.600
Nowhere.

12:09.520 --> 12:11.600
Just woke up. Head's not clear yet.

12:12.640 --> 12:13.480
What were you saying?

12:13.560 --> 12:14.800
I said

12:14.880 --> 12:16.840
Ning is being looked after
by the inn boys.

12:17.840 --> 12:19.000
I can manage the stall myself.

12:19.800 --> 12:21.640
It's fine. I'll go with you.

12:21.720 --> 12:24.240
-I need to stop by the bookshop anyway.
-Chunky Celery!

12:42.880 --> 12:44.640
Mr. and Mrs. Fan,

12:44.720 --> 12:45.880
I'm so sorry.

12:47.080 --> 12:48.960
Wrong way. This way.

12:49.600 --> 12:50.840
Serves me right.

12:56.000 --> 12:56.840
Are you hurt?

12:59.360 --> 13:00.240
I'm fine.

13:06.240 --> 13:07.320
NOODLES

13:18.720 --> 13:20.480
Why aren't you eating?

13:21.000 --> 13:21.840
You look distracted.

13:22.720 --> 13:24.400
Did the bookshop owner give you trouble?

13:26.320 --> 13:27.200
No.

13:31.800 --> 13:33.120
-The bill, please.
-Coming.

13:33.880 --> 13:36.520
That'll be 30 wen, sir.

13:36.600 --> 13:38.840
-I'll pay.
-All right.

13:39.360 --> 13:42.640
A grown man dining out
and letting a woman foot the bill.

13:43.160 --> 13:44.560
No shame at all.

13:47.800 --> 13:50.240
Must be living off her.

13:52.200 --> 13:53.720
I know him.

13:53.800 --> 13:56.160
That's the An family's
live-in husband. A kept man.

13:56.880 --> 13:59.880
Who knows what Mrs. An sees in him.

14:00.720 --> 14:02.360
Probably that pale face of his.

14:06.400 --> 14:07.400
Finished?

14:09.080 --> 14:11.360
-The bill, please.
-Right away.

14:13.760 --> 14:15.480
Twenty-one wen.

14:15.560 --> 14:17.480
Make it 20.

14:33.520 --> 14:34.800
Another pretty face living off someone?

14:35.760 --> 14:38.320
With that face, he could.

14:38.400 --> 14:39.240
Exactly.

14:41.960 --> 14:43.840
Did you overspend buying things for Ning?

14:45.480 --> 14:47.400
No, it's just…

14:47.480 --> 14:49.920
Looks like he doesn't know how to recover

14:50.000 --> 14:51.240
after Mr. An embarrassed himself.

14:59.280 --> 15:00.640
The coins are underneath.

15:05.280 --> 15:06.480
No need.

15:06.560 --> 15:08.080
I was worried they might not have change.

15:12.880 --> 15:15.400
Your New Year gift. Open it.

15:17.840 --> 15:19.600
Gold and silver are of no use to me.

15:22.080 --> 15:23.920
You're not taking it? Wait.

15:35.160 --> 15:36.000
Give it here.

15:36.880 --> 15:38.320
You've changed.

15:38.840 --> 15:41.040
-Marriage suits you.
-Why do you talk so much?

15:41.120 --> 15:42.400
Fine, fine. Take it.

15:42.920 --> 15:44.680
Sir, you must be joking.

15:44.760 --> 15:46.440
We're a small stall.

15:46.520 --> 15:48.600
We cannot break an ingot that size.

15:49.680 --> 15:50.800
I…

15:50.880 --> 15:52.360
-I have smaller change.
-That will do.

15:52.440 --> 15:53.800
We'll settle it with small silver.

15:53.880 --> 15:55.640
Much appreciated. Do come again.

15:55.720 --> 15:56.800
You keep it.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.640
Look at this young fellow.

16:01.720 --> 16:02.640
So young.

16:03.520 --> 16:04.960
I'll hold onto it for you.

16:05.040 --> 16:08.680
Could be some noble's son
wandering out here

16:08.760 --> 16:10.560
to see how common folk live.

16:10.640 --> 16:11.920
Perhaps.

16:15.480 --> 16:17.960
No one would bring an ingot
just to eat noodles.

16:18.480 --> 16:20.400
Where did you get that kind of money?

16:22.520 --> 16:24.800
Don't tell me the bookshop owner
gave it to you again.

16:24.880 --> 16:26.320
Just keep it.

16:27.040 --> 16:29.240
XIGU ALLEY

16:35.880 --> 16:37.040
Look, Changyu's back.

16:43.920 --> 16:46.520
You're finally back. Something's happened.

16:46.600 --> 16:47.560
What is it?

16:48.640 --> 16:50.440
The yamen suddenly ordered a levy.

16:50.520 --> 16:53.040
Grain and silver.

16:53.120 --> 16:54.720
By headcount.

16:54.800 --> 16:56.160
Four taels per person.

16:56.240 --> 16:57.600
That much?

16:58.120 --> 17:00.000
-That's daylight robbery.
-Exactly.

17:00.080 --> 17:01.520
We can manage ours.

17:01.600 --> 17:04.079
But the hired laborers and tenant farmers

17:04.160 --> 17:05.480
have no land, no savings.

17:05.560 --> 17:06.760
The New Year just passed.

17:06.839 --> 17:08.720
What are they supposed to do?

17:09.240 --> 17:11.240
-That's right.
-We won't survive this.

17:11.319 --> 17:15.160
I heard people from the next village
went to the yamen to beg.

17:15.240 --> 17:18.680
Kneeled there all day
and never even saw the magistrate.

17:20.200 --> 17:23.400
We can scrape together what we owe,

17:23.480 --> 17:24.880
but some families in Xigu Alley

17:24.960 --> 17:28.040
could empty their homes
and still not raise one tael.

17:28.119 --> 17:30.240
It's just after the holiday.

17:30.320 --> 17:31.760
Everyone's pockets are empty.

17:32.480 --> 17:34.080
I need to see Grandfather.

17:34.720 --> 17:37.720
With Uncle gone, who will cover his share?

17:38.840 --> 17:40.280
Do you want me to come?

17:42.080 --> 17:43.320
No.

17:43.400 --> 17:44.920
I'll go quietly and leave.

17:45.000 --> 17:46.800
I won't cross paths with that woman.

17:47.480 --> 17:49.280
You'd draw too much attention.

17:51.520 --> 17:55.440
Why is the county collecting
so much silver all of a sudden?

17:57.520 --> 17:58.520
When grain is levied,

17:59.640 --> 18:01.600
every county under Jizhou Prefecture

18:01.680 --> 18:03.120
receives the same decree.

18:03.800 --> 18:05.680
But grain and silver together

18:05.760 --> 18:06.800
is unheard of.

18:07.680 --> 18:10.000
Unless other counties are doing the same,

18:10.520 --> 18:14.120
this magistrate may be lining
his own purse.

18:16.560 --> 18:17.600
That's enough.

18:23.120 --> 18:23.960
Almost forgot.

18:28.720 --> 18:31.160
Slip this into Mrs. Zhao's room quietly.

18:31.760 --> 18:34.520
The New Year emptied everyone's coffers.

18:34.600 --> 18:35.760
I don't want them to worry.

18:37.400 --> 18:38.240
All right.

18:46.760 --> 18:49.240
Grain and silver both.

18:49.760 --> 18:51.720
They're pushing people into the grave.

18:54.120 --> 18:55.080
Some old relics

18:55.880 --> 18:58.200
can't carry, can't lift,

18:58.880 --> 19:03.760
just sit inside,
begging for food and water.

19:03.840 --> 19:06.440
They're a burden to the living.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.600
Exactly.

19:11.120 --> 19:14.280
An old man who refuses to die
is a thief of breath.

19:30.920 --> 19:31.760
Grandfather.

19:33.960 --> 19:34.960
Grandfather.

19:36.240 --> 19:37.080
Get up.

19:42.480 --> 19:43.360
Are you all right?

19:44.160 --> 19:46.960
Changyu, why are you here?

19:47.040 --> 19:49.640
Go. Leave.

19:51.240 --> 19:52.720
This useless old man

19:53.640 --> 19:57.560
brought this on himself.

20:02.000 --> 20:04.560
His son is dead,
and he still clings to this house.

20:04.640 --> 20:05.840
Shameless.

20:08.480 --> 20:10.320
I will drive him out

20:10.840 --> 20:12.920
sooner or later.

20:14.480 --> 20:15.320
Who's there?

20:17.160 --> 20:18.360
You jinx.

20:23.960 --> 20:24.800
‎What are you…

20:24.880 --> 20:27.040
Grandfather can't even get a sip of water,

20:27.560 --> 20:29.400
and you're eating meat?

20:29.480 --> 20:31.680
You… Get out!

20:31.760 --> 20:33.160
Pah!

20:34.120 --> 20:35.680
This house is mine.

20:35.760 --> 20:37.400
You leave.

20:38.080 --> 20:39.640
You and Uncle said it yourselves.

20:40.360 --> 20:41.280
Without a male heir,

20:42.000 --> 20:43.200
the house passes to the nearest kin.

20:44.160 --> 20:45.240
Your husband is dead.

20:45.320 --> 20:46.600
What right do you have to occupy it?

20:46.680 --> 20:49.120
My daughter can take in a husband.

20:49.200 --> 20:50.400
The Dayin Code states

20:51.440 --> 20:54.160
if a widow is unfilial, the grandfather
may dismiss her in his son's place.

20:56.000 --> 20:58.280
You cursed jinx.
I'll not hear another word--

21:00.960 --> 21:01.800
Fan Changyu.

21:01.880 --> 21:03.680
Striking an elder will land you in prison.

21:03.760 --> 21:05.240
Father! Father!

21:05.320 --> 21:08.320
Fan Changyu struck
your eldest daughter-in-law!

21:08.400 --> 21:10.040
She's assaulting me!

21:11.560 --> 21:13.560
Open your eyes and look.

21:14.280 --> 21:17.160
The deed bears my father's name.

21:18.160 --> 21:19.840
Grandfather can testify.

21:21.560 --> 21:24.000
What? That cannot be.

21:24.080 --> 21:26.720
I can remove you
from the Fan family this instant.

21:35.600 --> 21:37.840
Changyu, I beg you.

21:38.360 --> 21:40.560
Don't cast out a widow and her child.

21:41.320 --> 21:44.240
Your uncle's mourning period
has not even ended.

21:44.320 --> 21:47.920
-I'm begging you.
-What did you do while I was in mourning

21:48.000 --> 21:48.840
for my parents?

21:51.960 --> 21:53.640
Get out.

22:05.720 --> 22:06.560
Grandfather.

22:07.160 --> 22:09.880
Keep the deed with you.
Hide it somewhere safe.

22:11.400 --> 22:13.120
As for driving that family out,

22:13.760 --> 22:15.000
that's your call.

22:17.240 --> 22:18.600
Changyu.

22:20.200 --> 22:22.120
You're just like your father.

22:23.200 --> 22:25.280
Kind-hearted to a fault.

22:28.960 --> 22:31.480
Go on. Leave me be.

22:31.560 --> 22:33.720
Life and death are Heaven's will.

22:34.400 --> 22:36.440
I don't believe in Heaven's will.

22:36.520 --> 22:38.880
-Then come with me. Come home.
-Go.

22:39.480 --> 22:42.400
Even if I have to smash my head
against this wall, I won't go with you.

22:43.280 --> 22:46.480
I don't deserve it.

22:46.560 --> 22:48.880
Nonsense. What do you mean
you don't deserve it?

22:53.600 --> 22:57.560
Erniu wasn't my blood.

22:59.120 --> 23:01.880
I dragged your whole family into this.

23:03.040 --> 23:04.520
This is retribution.

23:06.080 --> 23:08.760
All of it.

23:12.040 --> 23:13.360
Seventeen years ago,

23:15.160 --> 23:18.120
your father brought your mother
to Xigu Alley.

23:19.120 --> 23:20.800
He paid me a large sum.

23:20.880 --> 23:25.040
Said he'd made enemies on escort duty

23:25.120 --> 23:26.560
and needed to lie low.

23:27.440 --> 23:30.320
My Erniu had been taken
as a child. Never found.

23:30.840 --> 23:32.040
So your father asked

23:32.120 --> 23:35.280
if he could register here
under the name Fan Erniu.

23:36.840 --> 23:38.800
So I told everyone

23:39.320 --> 23:41.400
my long-lost son

23:41.480 --> 23:43.520
had found his way home.

23:44.640 --> 23:46.800
The day before it happened,

23:47.880 --> 23:52.800
your parents came to see me.

23:54.080 --> 23:55.960
They left a letter

23:56.800 --> 23:58.600
and this deed.

23:59.720 --> 24:00.920
I asked him

24:01.440 --> 24:04.480
if the old enemy tracked him down.

24:05.320 --> 24:07.600
He would not answer.

24:07.680 --> 24:08.800
He only said

24:08.880 --> 24:11.160
that their deaths

24:11.240 --> 24:15.280
were the only way to ensure
you and Changning survived.

24:16.960 --> 24:18.320
You know your uncle.

24:19.080 --> 24:23.400
He'd fallen into gambling
these past years.

24:24.560 --> 24:26.840
After your father died,

24:26.920 --> 24:30.360
he stole the letter and burned it,

24:30.440 --> 24:33.400
trying to seize everything
your family owned.

24:34.880 --> 24:38.200
This old body of mine was useless.

24:38.800 --> 24:41.960
I couldn't stop him.

24:43.280 --> 24:45.920
Then your uncle met his end.

24:46.440 --> 24:48.280
Your aunt proved heartless.

24:49.000 --> 24:50.080
I told myself

24:50.840 --> 24:54.520
this was punishment for my selfishness.

25:01.840 --> 25:03.800
So Father and Mother
knew before they died.

25:04.320 --> 25:06.440
They knew they would not live long.

25:07.800 --> 25:09.000
But why would Father think

25:09.080 --> 25:11.360
that dying together with Mother
would protect me and Changning?

25:12.160 --> 25:14.520
And why does that differ
from what Lord Li said?

25:15.760 --> 25:17.440
What really happened?

25:22.840 --> 25:24.160
Why are you sitting here alone?

25:27.600 --> 25:28.600
Tell me something.

25:29.400 --> 25:31.080
Were my parents truly killed by bandits

25:32.040 --> 25:33.360
over a treasure map?

25:33.880 --> 25:34.880
Do you

25:35.600 --> 25:36.760
want to avenge them?

25:38.440 --> 25:39.280
I do.

25:39.960 --> 25:40.840
Even in my sleep.

25:42.240 --> 25:43.520
If the officials' conclusion

25:44.320 --> 25:45.840
turns out to be a lie,

25:45.920 --> 25:46.800
what would you do?

25:48.040 --> 25:49.640
Why would the authorities lie?

25:50.800 --> 25:54.120
Like your uncle colluding with Clerk Guo

25:54.200 --> 25:55.400
to swallow your estate.

25:55.480 --> 25:58.600
If even a county office
hides that kind of rot,

25:59.120 --> 26:00.360
then above it,

26:00.440 --> 26:04.200
prefecture, court,
the entanglements only grow denser.

26:05.400 --> 26:07.880
Factions. Colleagues.
Former classmates. In-laws.

26:08.560 --> 26:09.800
Officialdom in Dayin

26:10.760 --> 26:12.000
is a web spun tight.

26:12.840 --> 26:16.560
What does that have to do
with my parents' deaths?

26:20.000 --> 26:21.320
I am only saying.

26:25.720 --> 26:27.320
The imperial court may be vast,

26:27.840 --> 26:30.760
but at the end of the day,
it is just men holding office.

26:32.000 --> 26:33.040
However fiercely you protest,

26:33.560 --> 26:36.480
you are still placing your grievance
before the emperor.

26:37.480 --> 26:40.280
No matter who is involved
in my parents' deaths,

26:40.800 --> 26:41.800
I will keep digging.

26:42.640 --> 26:46.280
Web or no web, there is law.

26:46.360 --> 26:47.640
There is reason.

26:48.160 --> 26:50.560
If there isn't,
then this world truly falls apart.

26:55.120 --> 26:56.440
If I had been born a man,

26:57.400 --> 27:00.320
I might have taken the civil exams
or the military route,

27:00.400 --> 27:03.200
entered officialdom,
and cleared my parents' names myself.

27:07.120 --> 27:08.720
But I am only a woman.

27:10.280 --> 27:11.760
I cannot hold office.

27:11.840 --> 27:13.600
I know no powerful officials.

27:15.360 --> 27:16.960
The only path left is money.

27:19.800 --> 27:21.960
Money can turn even ghosts into laborers.

27:26.160 --> 27:28.160
The silver required
to make powerful men move

27:28.240 --> 27:29.560
will not be small.

27:30.840 --> 27:32.080
Every hurdle can be crossed.

27:32.160 --> 27:33.160
There will be a way.

27:39.240 --> 27:40.280
I've been meaning to ask.

27:40.800 --> 27:42.880
Is there something you want
for your birthday?

27:45.360 --> 27:46.920
I don't feel like celebrating this year.

27:48.880 --> 27:49.920
Name one wish.

27:50.440 --> 27:51.320
Consider it…

27:56.560 --> 27:59.120
Let it stand as your gift
for the years ahead.

28:01.280 --> 28:02.560
You're leaving?

28:13.560 --> 28:14.720
Do you have to leave?

28:25.360 --> 28:26.640
That was silly of me.

28:27.440 --> 28:28.880
It's not as if you won't return.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.080
Right?

29:01.800 --> 29:03.640
LI'S RESIDENCE

29:03.720 --> 29:06.400
My betrothal to the Grand Princess
is decided.

29:16.000 --> 29:19.680
Since Her Highness has given her word,
the match is settled.

29:19.760 --> 29:21.680
What difference does two years make?

29:25.720 --> 29:27.880
I thought you might be displeased,
since the wedding

29:27.960 --> 29:29.520
will not take place at once.

29:31.000 --> 29:32.560
After your sister entered the palace,

29:32.640 --> 29:35.000
and now with the Grand Princess
willing to marry into our family,

29:35.080 --> 29:38.480
our house will once again
stand at the height of honor.

29:38.560 --> 29:40.440
In this lifetime,

29:40.520 --> 29:42.200
that alone fulfills my wish.

29:44.960 --> 29:46.160
Ah, yes.

29:46.680 --> 29:49.720
An urgent dispatch arrived today.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.680
Take a look.

30:03.760 --> 30:04.920
Wei Xuan has detained General He?

30:12.000 --> 30:12.880
Forgive me.

30:14.200 --> 30:17.080
He is a loyal minister,
a capable commander, and my teacher.

30:17.920 --> 30:19.040
To see him treated so unjustly,

30:19.560 --> 30:20.880
I cannot remain idle.

30:23.720 --> 30:24.880
Then,

30:25.480 --> 30:26.800
you will leave tonight.

30:26.880 --> 30:29.600
Depart immediately and aid He Jingyuan.

30:29.680 --> 30:30.680
And while you are there,

30:31.280 --> 30:32.600
keep Wei Xuan in check.

30:33.880 --> 30:35.200
You don't mind him siding with Wei Yan?

30:37.720 --> 30:38.840
Wenkan,

30:39.760 --> 30:40.960
do you know

30:41.040 --> 30:43.440
how fragile the court stands now?

30:44.040 --> 30:45.640
Your teacher, He Jingyuan,

30:45.720 --> 30:48.800
is a man of unshakable loyalty.

30:49.440 --> 30:51.640
His heart is for the throne
and the people alone.

30:51.720 --> 30:53.600
He lowered his head to Wei Yan

30:53.680 --> 30:56.840
only because Wei Yan's suspicions
left him no choice.

30:56.920 --> 31:00.680
And now he sits in chains for it.

31:01.280 --> 31:02.440
So you believe

31:02.960 --> 31:04.520
Wei Yan is letting Wei Xuan act recklessly

31:05.040 --> 31:06.280
to isolate loyal officials?

31:08.840 --> 31:09.800
Once,

31:10.560 --> 31:13.280
Wei Yan and I
both served the Eastern Palace.

31:13.800 --> 31:15.800
We swore then

31:15.880 --> 31:18.320
to defend the realm of Dayin.

31:18.400 --> 31:21.680
Now he has grown
into a power unto himself,

31:21.760 --> 31:24.240
grasping at authority
and driving out all who oppose him.

31:24.880 --> 31:26.040
Our Li family

31:26.120 --> 31:28.920
has long been his biggest headache.

31:30.640 --> 31:32.240
I know

31:32.320 --> 31:34.000
you are like your teacher.

31:34.080 --> 31:35.320
You care for the people.

31:35.400 --> 31:37.480
You wish to shield the innocent.

31:37.560 --> 31:39.960
If you truly hope
to see your ideals realized,

31:40.480 --> 31:42.360
there is only one road forward.

31:43.160 --> 31:44.600
That is

31:44.680 --> 31:48.400
to uproot completely of Wei Yan
and the corrupt faction around him.

31:48.480 --> 31:50.920
Only then can the court be cleansed

31:51.000 --> 31:54.000
and the realm made secure.

31:57.200 --> 31:58.440
Wenkan,

31:59.720 --> 32:01.400
you are a good man.

32:01.480 --> 32:03.080
Your sense of loyalty

32:03.160 --> 32:04.880
is both your greatest strength

32:04.960 --> 32:08.600
and your gravest flaw.

32:10.600 --> 32:13.880
It is I who have drawn you into this.

32:17.640 --> 32:20.440
With all my heart, I'll give everything

32:20.520 --> 32:22.280
to help you bring down Wei Yan.

32:28.320 --> 32:31.160
Our northwest forces
are being pushed back at every turn.

32:31.240 --> 32:32.760
Wei Xuan has imprisoned He Jingyuan.

32:33.520 --> 32:35.880
He refuses orders and will not withdraw.

32:36.680 --> 32:39.640
He says that in the field, a general
answers to the war, not the court.

32:39.720 --> 32:40.920
He says he will regroup

32:41.520 --> 32:43.640
-and fight once more.
-Fight again?

32:46.560 --> 32:48.960
With weary troops and broken morale?

32:49.480 --> 32:52.360
In this freezing weather,
at the New Year's time?

32:52.440 --> 32:54.000
What battle does he imagine
he could fight?

32:59.280 --> 33:01.160
You. Take my command seal.

33:01.240 --> 33:03.880
Force him to hand command
back to He Jingyuan.

33:04.720 --> 33:05.720
Then,

33:06.600 --> 33:08.040
bind him and bring him back to me.

33:09.600 --> 33:10.440
Understood.

33:30.000 --> 33:30.960
Grandfather,

33:31.600 --> 33:33.880
Marquis Wu'an was ensnared
in the Chongzhou campaign.

33:33.960 --> 33:35.720
I have reliable source confirmed

33:35.800 --> 33:38.240
that Xie Zheng still lives.

33:38.920 --> 33:42.120
If we could join forces with him…

33:43.400 --> 33:44.520
He is not Wei Yan.

33:47.000 --> 33:49.840
Even if uncle and nephew
have fallen out as rumors say,

33:49.920 --> 33:52.600
blood ties do not sever so easily.

33:53.200 --> 33:54.320
Do not speak

33:54.920 --> 33:57.160
of winning over Marquis Wu'an again.

34:14.760 --> 34:16.239
Spread out. See if anyone is alive.

34:16.320 --> 34:17.159
-Yes.
-Yes.

34:22.960 --> 34:24.360
These were killed by Wei Xuan's troops.

34:25.760 --> 34:27.320
Such reckless slaughter

34:28.440 --> 34:30.159
is beyond reason.

34:31.719 --> 34:32.760
It was not Wei Xuan.

34:33.440 --> 34:35.600
I have men tracking his movements.

34:36.600 --> 34:38.400
Someone else is stirring the embers.

34:40.800 --> 34:43.040
-Quick. Send word to General He.
-At once.

35:03.200 --> 35:04.760
My lord, look.

35:05.480 --> 35:07.640
Footprints. Someone escaped.

35:09.040 --> 35:10.880
Or was one deliberately spared?

35:12.960 --> 35:15.040
Murder! Murder!

35:15.120 --> 35:17.640
They've slaughtered us!

35:17.720 --> 35:20.000
Good people, Ma Village is poor.
We could not pay

35:20.080 --> 35:21.680
the grain levy or silver tax.

35:22.360 --> 35:25.000
The village head led us
to the county yamen

35:25.080 --> 35:26.400
to beg for mercy.

35:27.560 --> 35:29.040
But halfway there,

35:29.120 --> 35:30.960
we were ambushed by county soldiers.

35:40.360 --> 35:42.880
I lay among the dead
and survived by chance.

35:44.240 --> 35:45.320
Brothers and sisters,

35:45.400 --> 35:47.760
we must gather every household.

35:47.840 --> 35:51.200
Come with me and demand justice
from that cursed official.

35:51.280 --> 35:52.280
Reclaim our grain!

35:52.360 --> 35:53.520
Take back our grain!

35:53.600 --> 35:55.280
-Demand justice!
-Demand justice!

35:55.360 --> 35:57.000
-Kill the corrupt official!
-Kill the corrupt official!

35:57.080 --> 35:59.080
-Take back our grain!
-Take back our grain!

36:09.360 --> 36:10.920
-General.
-Why have you come?

36:11.000 --> 36:13.160
Wei troops have slaughtered
innocent civilians.

36:14.400 --> 36:16.960
It seems Prince Changxin
has begun to move.

36:17.040 --> 36:22.320
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

36:22.400 --> 36:24.040
He was fine yesterday.

36:24.120 --> 36:25.920
Now he's dead just like that.

36:26.000 --> 36:27.120
-We can't just let this go.
-That's right.

36:27.200 --> 36:28.240
She should pay with her life.

36:28.320 --> 36:30.880
‎-Someone's gotta answer for this.
‎-The victim's at the door.

36:32.440 --> 36:35.440
-He ate here and died.
-Dead overnight.

36:35.520 --> 36:38.480
‎A grand place like this.

36:38.560 --> 36:40.560
Excuse me. What happened?

36:40.640 --> 36:41.800
You haven't heard?

36:41.880 --> 36:43.480
A man died after eating at Yixiang.

36:44.080 --> 36:46.520
His family's been here
since dawn demanding justice.

36:46.600 --> 36:48.640
Yixiang Restaurant is a den of murder.

36:48.720 --> 36:51.280
That woman running it
should be arrested and executed.

36:51.360 --> 36:53.520
Exactly. A life for a life.

36:53.600 --> 36:56.560
-Isn't that right?
-Right.

36:56.640 --> 36:57.840
A life for a life.

36:57.920 --> 37:00.600
Charging sky-high prices
and poisoning the food.

37:00.680 --> 37:02.280
Yesterday a guest suddenly collapsed.

37:02.360 --> 37:04.760
Ms. Yu thought it was epilepsy

37:04.840 --> 37:06.160
and sent for a doctor at once.

37:06.240 --> 37:08.920
The family was grateful at first.

37:09.000 --> 37:10.160
They took him home.

37:10.680 --> 37:12.520
Then he died in the night.

37:12.600 --> 37:13.720
This morning,

37:13.800 --> 37:15.800
they brought a coffin
and started making a scene.

37:15.880 --> 37:17.600
Saying we must pay with a life.

37:17.680 --> 37:19.600
It's obvious they're extorting her.

37:19.680 --> 37:20.760
-Exactly.
-Right.

37:21.520 --> 37:22.920
What did Qian say?

37:23.000 --> 37:25.040
She tried to reason with them,

37:25.120 --> 37:28.120
offered compensation
just to calm them down.

37:28.200 --> 37:30.920
But those bastards refused outright.

37:31.000 --> 37:32.440
They came looking for trouble.

37:32.520 --> 37:36.440
She suspects
another restaurant put them up to it.

37:36.520 --> 37:37.480
So she reported it.

37:37.560 --> 37:39.920
It's been quite some time,

37:40.000 --> 37:41.200
and still no word back.

37:41.280 --> 37:42.640
Isn't that infuriating?

37:42.720 --> 37:44.160
Of course it is.

37:44.240 --> 37:45.880
-That bastard.
-Someone's targeting her.

37:46.480 --> 37:48.120
So what do we do?

37:48.200 --> 37:50.080
We can't just stand here waiting.

37:52.760 --> 37:53.800
I have a plan.

37:53.880 --> 37:56.440
But first, draw the bailiffs
away from the entrance.

38:00.840 --> 38:02.880
Disgraceful.

38:07.600 --> 38:08.480
See those three?

38:09.000 --> 38:10.000
The loudest ones.

38:10.080 --> 38:12.400
The one with stubble. The one in the cap.

38:13.200 --> 38:14.320
The one in black.

38:20.600 --> 38:22.680
Never coming here again.

38:22.760 --> 38:24.000
-Never.
-Unbelievable!

38:24.080 --> 38:25.960
They owe us an explanation.

38:26.040 --> 38:28.080
I've long heard the owner

38:28.160 --> 38:29.920
-dabbles in shady tricks.
-Now!

38:30.000 --> 38:32.240
‎Hey, what are you doing?

38:34.120 --> 38:36.800
A debt must be paid.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.240
Never seen a gambling house

38:38.320 --> 38:39.520
collect before?

38:39.600 --> 38:40.560
Get lost. All of you.

38:41.360 --> 38:42.320
Go.

38:44.560 --> 38:45.600
Take it away.

38:51.200 --> 38:52.200
Don't try anything.

39:09.600 --> 39:10.640
Talk.

39:11.400 --> 39:13.880
Who sent you to stir up trouble
at Yixiang Restaurant?

39:17.760 --> 39:20.120
No one sent us.

39:20.200 --> 39:22.600
Someone died eating here.

39:22.680 --> 39:24.480
Are we not allowed to ask for justice?

39:24.560 --> 39:26.480
You've bound us here.

39:26.560 --> 39:27.400
What's next, kill us?

39:27.480 --> 39:29.880
Silence everyone for good?

39:30.480 --> 39:32.760
This place isn't a restaurant.

39:32.840 --> 39:36.240
-It's a butcher's den. A slaughterhouse.
-That's right.

39:36.320 --> 39:37.560
A death trap--

39:42.720 --> 39:44.120
You talk too much.

39:47.960 --> 39:49.480
That tongue's quick.

39:51.480 --> 39:53.200
Cut it out and feed it to the dogs.

39:53.280 --> 39:54.200
No, wait.

39:54.720 --> 39:57.000
Heroine, that's against the law.

39:57.520 --> 39:58.600
-Heroine.
-Wait up.

40:00.520 --> 40:02.880
-Cut it for real.
-Heroine, have mercy!

40:03.640 --> 40:04.600
Of course.

40:16.880 --> 40:18.680
He struggled too much.

40:19.280 --> 40:20.320
Didn't get the whole thing.

40:21.280 --> 40:22.280
Just a piece.

40:23.520 --> 40:25.280
Pig tongue does look convincing.

40:26.360 --> 40:27.360
Bring a dog.

40:28.400 --> 40:29.320
Feed it.

40:50.440 --> 40:51.440
Now.

40:51.520 --> 40:52.840
Who put you up to this?

40:53.840 --> 40:55.160
Lie once,

40:55.240 --> 40:58.640
and your tongues feed the dogs too.

40:59.360 --> 41:00.720
-I'll talk.
-I'll talk.

41:00.800 --> 41:01.680
-I'll talk.
-Let me go first.

41:01.760 --> 41:03.680
-I'll talk.
-Let me go first.

41:03.760 --> 41:04.720
-Let me go first.
-I'll talk.

41:04.800 --> 41:05.760
Enough.

41:06.920 --> 41:08.520
-You.
-It was Clerk Guo.

41:08.600 --> 41:10.520
One of his attendants came to us.

41:16.120 --> 41:16.960
You're lying.

41:17.040 --> 41:19.400
Milady, we swear we're not.

41:19.480 --> 41:22.240
It was Clerk Guo's attendant who found us.

41:24.360 --> 41:26.840
Clerk Guo has no quarrel with Yixiang.

41:27.360 --> 41:28.480
Why would he do this?

41:29.240 --> 41:31.320
-We don't know.
-Still playing dumb?

41:31.400 --> 41:33.760
Men! Cut their tongues.

41:33.840 --> 41:34.920
We don't know.

41:35.000 --> 41:37.120
We truly don't. We really don't know.

41:37.200 --> 41:39.120
-We're telling the truth.
-Let them go.

41:46.040 --> 41:48.640
You're not dragging them to court?

41:49.760 --> 41:51.080
You heard them.

41:51.160 --> 41:53.160
Clerk Guo was behind it.

41:55.920 --> 41:58.000
So a rival restaurant

41:58.080 --> 42:01.360
bribed Clerk Guo to frame Yixiang?

42:03.440 --> 42:04.280
It's worse.

42:04.960 --> 42:06.680
Worse how?

42:10.200 --> 42:11.720
Yixiang may not survive this.

42:12.680 --> 42:14.920
I've spent half the day calling in favors.

42:15.000 --> 42:16.360
Not a single door opened.

42:17.440 --> 42:20.320
Even Magistrate Cui refuses to see me.

42:25.600 --> 42:27.480
My family has ties with Constable Wang.

42:27.560 --> 42:29.960
I'll go beg him to help.

42:30.040 --> 42:31.000
Don't.

42:32.720 --> 42:34.520
I appreciate it.

42:34.600 --> 42:36.280
But don't involve Constable Wang.

42:36.360 --> 42:37.520
You'll drag him into trouble.

42:40.160 --> 42:41.280
Ms. Yu, trouble.

42:41.360 --> 42:43.120
The bailiffs just stormed in
from the back.

42:43.840 --> 42:45.080
I'm going now.

42:45.160 --> 42:48.520
I'll go as well. Let's see who they are
and what they're after.

42:49.040 --> 42:51.400
Don't defend me.
You'll end up in court for nothing.

42:52.480 --> 42:54.040
I know Magistrate Cui.

42:54.120 --> 42:55.400
I can handle him.

42:56.000 --> 42:57.600
What matters is this.

42:57.680 --> 43:00.360
Stay here. Do not let anyone near Bao'er.

43:08.960 --> 43:10.680
You are the proprietress of Yixiang?

43:11.320 --> 43:12.160
I am.

43:12.720 --> 43:13.600
Take her.

43:15.960 --> 43:18.440
Fine. I'll go to the yamen with you.

46:14.400 --> 46:17.600
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:17.680 --> 46:18.600
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
